# Public content layer — committed so Vercel can render it (V3-7 fix 2026-04-30):
#   vault/blogs/   — published blog posts read by lib/vault.ts at build time
#   vault/courses/ — published course outlines + chapters read by lib/courses.ts
# Private operational layer — NOT committed (raw research, internal cost data, audit logs):
vault/research/**/*.md
vault/decisions/**/*.md
vault/retrospectives/**/*.md
vault/_index/**/*.md
vault/_audit/**/*.md
vault/marketing/**/*.md
